oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ben Ellis
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Ben Ellis (Tellico guide), in hat with overalls, plowing corn with a mule on Coker Creek. Two other people, wearing hats, can be seen in the back of the field. Rows of plants, contained by fence, can be seen near a wooden structure in the background.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
